blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### What happened?\r\n\r\nWhen using any of the build options as template variables in an `universal_binaries`  post command it results in a error.\r\n\r\n```\r\nтип release failed after 14.88s error=post hook failed: template: tmpl:1:19: executing \"tmpl\" at <.Path>: map has no entry for key \"Path\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### How can we reproduce this?\r\n\r\n```yml\r\nuniversal_binaries:\r\n  - replace: true\r\n    hooks:\r\n      post: ./post.sh {{ .Path }} {{ .Target }} {{ .Version }}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### goreleaser version\r\n\r\n```bash\r\ngoreleaser version 1.4.1\r\ncommit: a1447a363579365f489458ad7636fd088a5b66ab\r\nbuilt by: homebrew\r\ngoos: darwin\r\ngoarch: amd64\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### GoReleaser Check\r\n\r\n- [X] goreleaser check shows no errors\r\n\r\n### Search\r\n\r\n- [X] I did search for other open and closed issues before opening this.\r\n\r\n### Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nThe example docs show that it should be possible...\r\nhttps://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/blob/4a4c5ec5a636856ea44c302333e12a5a592e3938/www/docs/customization/universalbinaries.md?plain=1#L43\r\n\r\nLooking at the code, `WithBuildOptions` is never called on the template like it is on a regular build.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/blob/f585f3be698ae1d3b86895a6f082518483283d94/internal/pipe/build/build.go#L125\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/blob/f585f3be698ae1d3b86895a6f082518483283d94/internal/pipe/universalbinary/universalbinary.go#L82","closed_by":{"login":"caarlos0","id":245435,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NTQzNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/245435?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0","html_url":"https://github.com/caarlos0","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/user